    ('2047269028301767078', 'twitter', 'dhh', 'https://x.com/dhh/status/2047269028301767078', 'Thu Apr 23 10:59:07 +0000 2026', '2026-04-23 13:10:46', NULL, 'With the Vantablack theme tweaked for true blacks in Omarchy 3.6, I''ve gotten the 16" Dell XPS OLED down to an incredible 2.2w idle. A pixel off is a pixel that doesn''t gulp power. Gotta love it! https://t.co/QXMmf3zvyt', 'en', 594, 26, 11, 21492, 3, 'Personal technical achievement with OLED power optimization', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
